 *https://www.codewars.com/kata/55685cd7ad70877c23000102/train/java
 *Java
 * 
 *In this simple assignment you are given a number and have to make it negative. Negative numbers require no modifications.
 */

//Codewars answer
public class Kata {
  public static int makeNegative(final int x) {
    
    return Math.abs(x) * (-1); // Your code here.
   
  }
}
